Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.68,0:23:41.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說你也來幫忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.17,0:23:45.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,游離子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.54,0:23:50.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,游離子  是誰幹的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.68,0:23:52.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天使
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.83,0:23:53.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天使？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.07,0:23:59.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  奏一直和我在一起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.45,0:24:11.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天使…
